import React from 'react'
import { AddressCheckout, BagCheckout, Container, DotsCheckout, Logo, NavCheckOutSteps, NavContainer, NavLogo, NavSecure } from './Cart.element'

const Cart = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <NavContainer>
        <NavLogo>
          <Logo src="https://images.indianexpress.com/2021/01/myntra.png" />
        </NavLogo>
        <NavCheckOutSteps>
        <BagCheckout>BAG</BagCheckout>
        <DotsCheckout>---------</DotsCheckout>
        <AddressCheckout></AddressCheckout>


        </NavCheckOutSteps>
        <NavSecure></NavSecure>
      </NavContainer>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default Cart
